\begin_layout Section
Results
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The plots show an approximate inverse square relationship between `
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

' and `
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

', since the obtained slope
\begin_inset Formula $=1.8<2$
\end_inset

 even after considering the errors.
\end_layout

